name: Stance Socks Moorland Wool
description: Its premium merino wool offers a plush ride and helps regulate temperatures. And to further cradle your feet in comfort, the sock features a deep heel pocket, elastic arch support, and medium cushioning. One look at the Moorland and you know it’s ready for winter.

name: Stance Socks Mahalo
description: Thanks to the sock’s luxurious combed cotton and deep heel pocket, your feet can kick back in comfort. Mesh vents help them stay cool while the sock’s reinforced heel and toe provide a plush ride and additional durability.

name: Stance Socks Hayes
description: Its mercerized cotton provides a beautiful luster while its elastic arch and deep heel pocket offer plenty of comfort. Thanks to the Hayes, you can start your day in luxury.

name: Stance Socks Waipio
description:
Beaches, palm trees, and surf shacks. 
Thanks to its mercerized cotton and deep heel pocket, this premium dress sock offers a crisp appearance and an abundance of comfort. It’s the sock of choice for those who would rather be at the beach.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Essentials Wash Kit
description: Formulated naturally, this essentials kit comes with Shampoo, Conditioner, a bar of Uppercut's famous goats milk soap and a branded black pocket comb.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Pomade + Shave Combo Pack
description: This essentials shave kit comes with Shave Cream, Aftershave Moisturizer and a tin of Uppercut Deluxe Pomade.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Matt Clay
description:
Uppercut Deluxe Matt Clay makes it easy to achieve a no-fuss messy look. Don’t let the thick consistency fool you, the clay does what you tell it to, effortlessly piecing out hair to give a pliable, re-workable style.

Directions for use: Spread a small amount in dry palms and fingers and work through dry hair, styling as desired.

Size: 70g.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Featherweight
description:
Featherweight has plenty of tack and dry finish for a natural looking hold. This product is that it’s water soluble which means you get a great dry look without any build up or residue. Without a doubt the great all rounder for textured styles

Size: 70g.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Pomade
description:
Uppercut Deluxe Pomade's unique formula means it will wash out easily leaving no residue. The Pomade gives control and definition without the weight of traditional pomades.

Directions for use: Rub a small amount into palms and work through dry hair to style as desired.

Size: 100ml.
